'''Ediya Coffee''' is a [[caf<U+00E9>|coffee shop]] chain in [[South Korea]]. As of 2013, the chain has over 1,000 retail stores in South Korea.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/biz/2014/03/328_146361.html | title=Ediya goes after Asian coffee drinkers | publisher=''[[The Korea Times]]'' | date=November 17, 2013 | accessdate=13 December 2014 | author=Hyo-sik, Lee}}</ref>

